{"type":"message","id":"52a53df0","parentId":"230a0566","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:39:02.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me create the experiment design file.","thinkingSignature":"aa786e309b4ec28dfd6db5bfd8f16d489f685f7c8f6d417f4976c64c3cd6e558"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pfznbp7p5zd7_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Experiment\n\n## Hypothesis\n**Formula:** `score(T) = CFI(T) × (freq(T)/120)`\n\nThis hybrid score should:\n- **Suppress constant-format tokens** (freq≈160, CFI=1): score = 1.0 × (160/120) = 1.33 (over threshold → EXCLUDE)\n- **Select research trajectory tokens** (freq<120, CFI>0.5): score < 0.5 × 1.0 < 0.5 (→ INCLUDE)\n\n## Expected Outcomes\n\n| Token Type | freq | CFI | score | Decision |\n|------------|------|-----|-------|----------|\n| \"for next instantiation\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | EXCLUDE |\n| \"pulse\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | EXCLUDE |\n| \"completed at:\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | EXCLUDE |\n| \"Phase 1\" | 136 | 0.96 | 1.09 | EXCLUDE |\n| \"architecture\" | 80 | 0.65 | 0.43 | INCLUDE |\n| \"compression\" | 45 | 0.58 | 0.22 | INCLUDE |\n| \"temporal\" | 30 | 0.45 | 0.11 | EXCLUDE |\n\n## Experiment Design\n\n### Dataset\n- 200 pulses from `pulse_archive/`\n- 80/20 train/test split (160/40)\n\n### Metrics\n- **Precision**: % of selected tokens that are true research concepts\n- **Recall**: % of true research concepts captured\n- **F1**: Harmonic mean\n\n### Comparison Baselines\n1. Binary CFI ≥ 0.7 AND freq < 60 (from CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md)\n2. Binary CFI ≥ 0.5 AND freq ∈ [3, 120)\n\n### Proposed Threshold\n- score(T) > 0.15 AND score(T) < 1.0 → INCLUDE\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\experiments\\HYBRID_CFI_FREQ_experiment.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2528,"output":509,"cacheRead":12245,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cache